==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmantle
<hw>Un*man"tle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>mantle</ets>.]</ety> <def>To divest of a mantle;
to uncover.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Nay, she said, but I will <qex>unmantle</qex> you.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmarry</ent>⟦br⟧
